00:08.216 --> 00:10.594
<i>to move on.</i>

00:10.594 --> 00:13.096
<i>And then,</i>

00:10.594 --> 00:13.096
<i>the strangest thing happened.</i>

00:13.096 --> 00:15.182
I love you, so much.

00:15.182 --> 00:17.017
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:

00:15.182 --> 00:17.017
<i>I know. Whoa, right?</i>

00:17.017 --> 00:20.020
<i>But here's the thing:</i>

00:17.017 --> 00:20.020
<i>Rafael wanted to be with Petra,</i>

00:20.020 --> 00:21.939
<i>but Petra was hesitant,</i>

00:20.020 --> 00:21.939
<i>because, well...</i>

00:21.939 --> 00:23.315
