00:23.315 --> 00:25.734
these two happy kids.

00:25.734 --> 00:28.111
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:

00:25.734 --> 00:28.111
<i>Plus, she had this new thing</i>

00:25.734 --> 00:28.111
<i>going with Chuck,</i>

00:28.111 --> 00:30.364
<i>the owner of</i>

00:28.111 --> 00:30.364
<i>the Fairwick Hotel next door.</i>

00:30.364 --> 00:32.449
<i>But eventually,</i>

00:30.364 --> 00:32.449
<i>Raf won her over.</i>

00:32.449 --> 00:34.702
<i>Yeah, he can be</i>

00:32.449 --> 00:34.702
<i>pretty relentless.</i>

00:34.702 --> 00:36.954
<i>Which brings me</i>

00:34.702 --> 00:36.954
<i>to his sister, Luisa.</i>

00:36.954 --> 00:38.873
<i>See, he didn't quite trust her,</i>

00:38.873 --> 00:40.749
<i>or her new girlfriend, Eileen.</i>

