00:40.749 --> 00:42.543
in my sister's life,

00:42.543 --> 00:43.961
we need to do

00:42.543 --> 00:43.961
some medical tests.

00:43.961 --> 00:45.629
<i>And it turns out,</i>

00:43.961 --> 00:45.629
<i>Raf was right</i>

00:45.629 --> 00:47.046
<i>to be suspicious, because...</i>

00:47.046 --> 00:48.465
You do realize,

00:47.046 --> 00:48.465
when you pass

00:48.465 --> 00:50.258
this medical exam,

00:48.465 --> 00:50.258
you leave the country.

00:50.258 --> 00:52.260
Or I will have you

00:50.258 --> 00:52.260
