00:52.260 --> 00:53.929
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:

00:52.260 --> 00:53.929
<i>Yup, that's right:</i>

00:53.929 --> 00:57.307
<i>Eileen was really</i>

00:53.929 --> 00:57.307
<i>the crime lord Sin Rostro.</i>

00:57.307 --> 00:58.976
<i>Which brings us to Scott.</i>

00:58.976 --> 01:01.186
<i>I mean, dead Scott.</i>

01:01.186 --> 01:03.772
<i>See, the police recently</i>

01:01.186 --> 01:03.772
<i>identified his killer,</i>

01:03.772 --> 01:04.982
